---
// Price Floor Effect Visualization
---

<div class="chart-container">
  <div class="chart-header">
    <h3>Government Price Floor Effect</h3>
    <p class="chart-subtitle">How Government Ownership Creates Asset Support</p>
  </div>
  <div class="price-floor-visual">
    <div class="market-section">
      <div class="market-label">Free Market Volatility</div>
      <div class="volatility-line">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 300 120" class="volatility-svg">
          <path d="M10 60 Q50 20 90 60 T170 40 T250 60 T290 80" 
                stroke="rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.8)" 
                stroke-width="3" 
                fill="none" 
                class="market-line"/>
          <text x="150" y="100" text-anchor="middle" class="svg-text">High Volatility</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="arrow-down">â†“</div>
    
    <div class="floor-section">
      <div class="market-label">With Government Floor</div>
      <div class="floor-line">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 300 120" class="floor-svg">
          <!-- Price floor line -->
          <line x1="10" y1="80" x2="290" y2="80" 
                stroke="rgba(90, 107, 93, 0.9)" 
                stroke-width="4" 
                stroke-dasharray="5,5"/>
          <!-- Market line above floor -->
          <path d="M10 70 Q50 50 90 65 T170 55 T250 65 T290 70" 
                stroke="rgba(69, 90, 100, 0.8)" 
                stroke-width="3" 
                fill="none" 
                class="supported-line"/>
          <!-- Floor area -->
          <rect x="10" y="80" width="280" height="30" 
                fill="rgba(90, 107, 93, 0.2)" 
                class="floor-area"/>
          <text x="150" y="100" text-anchor="middle" class="svg-text">Government Support Floor</text>
          <text x="150" y="35" text-anchor="middle" class="svg-text">Reduced Volatility</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="chart-insight">
    <div class="insight-icon">ðŸ’¡</div>
    <div class="insight-content">
      <strong>Key Insight:</strong> When governments hold assets as strategic reserves, they have strong incentives to support prices. 
      This creates an implicit "floor" that didn't exist before.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .chart-container {
    background: rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.9);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(90, 107, 93, 0.15);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(45, 45, 45, 0.06);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .chart-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .chart-header h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--charcoal-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .chart-subtitle {
    color: var(--shadow-subtle);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .price-floor-visual {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .market-section, .floor-section {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .market-label {
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--charcoal-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .volatility-svg, .floor-svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 120px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--warm-light) 0%, var(--cream-warm) 100%);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .svg-text {
    font-size: 12px;
    fill: var(--shadow-subtle);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }

  .market-line {
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }

  .supported-line {
    animation: stable 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .floor-area {
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .arrow-down {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--sage-green);
    margin: 1rem 0;
    animation: bounce 1.5s infinite;
  }

  .chart-insight {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cream-warm) 0%, var(--mist-light) 100%);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--sage-green);
  }

  .insight-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .insight-content {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--charcoal-light);
  }

  .insight-content strong {
    color: var(--steel-blue);
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0% { opacity: 0.7; }
    100% { opacity: 1; }
  }

  @keyframes stable {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-2px); }
  }

  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    40% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
    60% { transform: translateY(-5px); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .volatility-svg, .floor-svg {
      height: 100px;
    }
    
    .svg-text {
      font-size: 10px;
    }
  }
</style>